Creating a Kafka Topic
$ docker-compose exec kafka kafka-topics.sh --create --topic baeldung_linux
  --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1 --bootstrap-server kafka:9092


To build to a Docker daemon, use:
  mvn compile com.google.cloud.tools:jib-maven-plugin:3.4.0:dockerBuild

$ docker-compose exec kafka kafka-topics.sh --create --topic messages
  --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1 --bootstrap-server kafka:9092

mvn compile jib:dockerBuild


docker image prune

